column5:
We will be hosting interviews in the following weeks (starting next Sunday practice)! I know interviews sound scary, but these are informal and are just for getting to know you better, so don't worry!

We are planning to hold them 15 minutes before and 30 minutes after the next few tryout practices, so please let us know your availability! Also, we will be confirming these interview times soon, so be on the lookout for a confirmation email.
column6: If you have any time preferences for the interview, or if you have additional comments about availability, let us know here! (for example, you would prefer going before Week 3 tryouts, you can only stay 15 minutes after Day 4 Tryouts, etc.)
